import React from 'react';
import { Container, Screen, Previous, Current, Button } from './Styled'


export default function Calculator() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Screen>
                <Previous></Previous>
                <Current></Current>
            </Screen>
            <Button gridSpan={2}>AC</Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button></Button>
            <Button gridSpan ={2}>=</Button>
            

        </Container>
        
    )
}
